```python
def fib(n):
    if n <= 1:
        return n
    if not hasattr(fib, 'memo'):
        fib.memo = {}
    if n not in fib.memo:
        fib.memo[n] = fib(n-1) + fib(n-2)
    return fib.memo[n]
```
